{"tid":370650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台：考慮黃昏前改發三號風球","createTime":"2017-08-23T06:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T06:54:50.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d2efe1efffde384c566fa34567b18b010c1a3d","tid":370650,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:54:50.000Z","msg":"八號東南烈風或暴風信號現正生效，天文台表示，隨着強颱風「天鴿」逐漸遠離，本港風力正在減弱，但本港西南部仍然吹烈風，高地更吹暴風，當本港風勢減弱的趨勢持續，天文台會考慮在黃昏前改發三號強風信號。<br />\n<br />\n下午3時，「天鴿」集結在香港以西約140公里，預料向西北偏西移動，時速約25公里，移入廣東內陸，並逐漸減弱。<br />\n<br />\n過去一小時，沙洲及赤鱲角分別錄得的最高持續風速為每小時86及65公里，最高陣風分別為每小時103及99公里。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170823/s00001/1503470862167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170823%2Fs00001%2F1503470862167&d=nO9b1a1YD2by4zN8IxcPMm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8d982678\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170823%2Fs00001%2F1503470862167&h=f750d048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170823/s00001/1503470862167</a>"}]}